xample, if a patient dresses in the morning, puts on a prosthetic device later in the day, and then \n\nundresses in the evening, code based on the type and amount of assistance required to complete the entire \ndressing activity, even if portions occur in the morning, evening or throughout the day. \n\nGG0130F Upper body dressing \n\nDEFINITION", "type": "Document"}}